social_posts.post_text: No need to reinvent the wheel when it comes to hitting☝🏽 Mixing in shorter distances and varying pitch speeds can help hitters stay adjustable too. Here’s one example of what that might look like from @angels outfielder and MY GUYY🤩 @bossmanboyd (aka “MARSHAWN LYNCH”🏈). BJ knows his own swing extremely well and stays within himself. He can hit homers, but he values consistent hard contact more than raw power😤 His swing works from the top down, so he’s more of a hands and shoulders guy than trying to generate a ton of ground force like some other hitters do @mattswope19 Whatever works works… just be yourself and own it🫡🏊🏽‍♂️💦⚾️ @baymanish_ @top_tier_california facility: @catchingacademy #baseball #practice #hit #seeds #littleleague #college #mlb #compete #havefun #respect #thegame #staypositive #workhard #smile #beyourself #focus #shine #neverforget #teammates #baseballislife #myguy
